ighlight>barrels</color> were launched into the Sea of Flames, with some landing quite deep inside.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Sigh... I feel ashamed to admit this, but we can't get them out from there...","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"I guess... You'll have to go get those barrels yourselves.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005},{"text":"Yeah, I'll share them with you.","quest_name":"We Promise, We Deliver","quest_id":122000005}]}